Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.59,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Fighting back again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:41.92,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Seems to be like it never ends
